text: Stowaway is a 1936 American musical movie directed by William A. Seiter and starring Shirley Temple, Robert Young, Alice Faye, Helen Westley, Allan Lane, Astrid Allwyn, Eugene Pallette, Philip Ahn. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1936 musical movies Category:1930s American musical movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by William A. Seiter
